Event Rental
Party Rentals
Whether it is a corporate outing, birthday party, anniversary, wedding reception or holiday party, Sweet Sixteen, Quinceanera, Bar/Bat Mitzvah or Retirement Party, Village Golf Club can accommodate your party. We provide a setting like no other with our beautiful golf course views. Our party room can accommodate up to 100 people with a dance floor. Our party packages include four hours of room rental time as well as additional time for set up and clean up.
Additionally, we have a beautiful outdoor ceremony area available. We cater to your needs by offering several different food and beverage options. Guests are free to use their caterer of choice, while beverages must be purchased at our facility. We allow you to decorate the room to your liking to create the themed party you have been dreaming of. With the friendliest staff around, Village Golf Club is truly the place to host your party! To see our beautiful space please call (561) 793-1400 to speak with Dan.
